thread.title: Jon Jennings
thread.title_full: Eagle Optics reviewed by Jon Jennings

author: Jon Jennings
title: Jon Jennings
text: The Point Lobos State Reserve in California has been doing business with Eagle Optics for over ten years. Eagle Optics has always provided excellent customer service when ordering new binoculars and spotting scopes and inquiring about service and repairs. Their warranty is second to none. High quality equipment and fair prices.
